N = lambda x, y : {(x-1,y), (x+1,y), (x,y-1), (x,y+1)}
S = set()
x, y = 0, 0
key = False
for j in input():
    K = N(x, y)
    if j == 'L': y -= 1
    if j == 'R': y += 1
    if j == 'D': x -= 1
    if j == 'U': x += 1
    if (x, y) in S:
        print("WR")
        key = True
        break
    S |= K
if key == False:
    print("OK")
